  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13086827/site-masthead.jpg" alt="Summer 2022 price freeze" /></p>
<p>We’re thrilled to announce that <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/lakes-mountains-holidays/summer-2022"><strong>Summer 2022 is on sale now</strong></a>.</p>
<p>Now, more than ever, we all want to make the most of life. That’s why we’re inviting you to experience more on your next summer holiday with Inghams.</p>
<p>Whether that’s by doing more on a walking holiday in <a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Austria</a>, discovering more whilst living the culture in <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a>, or hearing more of the sounds of nature in <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>. Life is filled with surprising, extraordinary, breathtaking moments, and we want you to experience them to the fullest.</p>
<h3><span class="page-title">Price freeze!</span></h3>
<h3><span class="geolocation-title">Book your summer 2022 holiday at 2021 prices*</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">After the year we’ve all had, we know not everyone will feel ready to travel during summer 2021 - that’s why we’re committing to a summer 2022 price freeze. We’ll make sure you’re not paying over the odds for your next adventure despite increased customer demand. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Due to the continued uncertainty around travel for Summer 2021, we have decided to extend our Summer 2022 Price Freeze Offer until 30th April. Now you have more time to secure your Summer 2022 holiday at 2021 prices.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
