<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13086829/landing-page2.jpg" alt="In Safe Hands" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you’d like to get something in the diary for summer 2021, we’re here to help you re-discover your passions and plan your holiday around them. To help keep you and your money safe we've put measures in place so you can enjoy total peace of mind this summer. </span></p>
<p><strong>Your money's safe </strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If we have to cancel your holiday because of Covid-19, you can pick another trip or get your money back.</span></p>
<p><strong>Flexible bookings</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There's no amendment fee until the date your final balance is due, which is now just 4 weeks before departure for all summer 2021 departures**. </span></p>
<p><strong>With you at every step</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you want any advice, just call us and we'll help. While you're away, our local staff will be there to support you if you need it.</span></p>
