<p> </p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">*Applies to new bookings, plus existing S21 bookings who want to move to S22. Valid on new bookings &amp; movers until 30th April.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">** If any of our partners do charge an amendment fee, we might have to pass on the cost to you. All Summer 2021 holiday balances have been delayed until 4 weeks before departure. </span></p>]]></bodyText>
